description	"B1 Battle Droid 

Class Summary: 
A multi-life class with a rapid-fire marksman rifle, permanent radar sense, and a small arsenal of explosive weapons.

Weaponry:
- E-5s Marksman Rifle (Based on A280 level 3)
- E-60R Rocket Launcher (1)
- Frag Grenade (1)
- Concussion Grenade (1)

Abilities:
- Reinforcements (2)
- Assemble
- Gunbash
- Radar (Perma-sense 1)
- Computer Link (can see ally health and ammo)
- Blast Armor

B1-Series battle droids were battle droids that made up the backbone of the Trade Federation Droid Army and the Separatist Droid Army."